description:
This alignment contains semantic mappings between EuroVoc and Agrovoc, the multilingual agricultural thesaurus of the FAO (Food and Agriculture Organization). 
The total number of mappings in the dataset amounts to 1,378 including 1,318 "exactMatch", 45 "broadMatch",  6 "narrowMatch", 5 "closeMatch" and 4 "relatedMatch".
title: Semantic alignment - EuroVoc - Agrovoc
name: eurovoc_agrovoc
contact_address: Publications Office of the EU, 2, rue Mercier, L-2985 Luxembourg
